    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2e53f6cae7007c542bf78e3dab4cdc90, type: 3}
  - text: "Bazen bir okul \xE7\u0131k\u0131\u015F\u0131nda, bazense adliye koridorlar\u0131nda
      bana her yerde rastlayabilirsiniz, \xE7eketimi a\xE7t\u0131m m\u0131 envai
      \xE7e\u015Fit \xFCr\xFCne ula\u015Fabilirsiniz"
    emotion: 3
    expression: {fileID: 8179892458493602980, guid: f2304ce7664feea448c58dba784a15bb, type: 3}
    voiceLine: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d5058d277ba364b44874127a6fb533b1, type: 3}
